# Vendored upstream: Google's open-source robots.txt matcher
# (https://github.com/google/robotstxt, Apache-2.0). Carried verbatim and
# validated by the upstream-conformance test suite (tests/testthat/
# test-upstream-matcher-cases-r9.R, test-cucumber.R), not by this package's own
# line coverage. reporting_robots.{cc,h} is the upstream reporting layer, which
# the package deliberately does not use (it collects directives via its own
# DirectiveCollector in src/collector_binding.cpp). Excluded so coverage
# reflects the package's own code.
src/robots.cc
src/robots.h
src/reporting_robots.cc
src/reporting_robots.h
